  "1904480": {
    "name": "绝对魔权",
    "steam_appid": 1904480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/5a4e142e0844a19b2561ca110f5e51ed.avif?t=1771265568\" width=584 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/2542cd4f88020c0bd98d336202c5e533.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/2542cd4f88020c0bd98d336202c5e533.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由重新定义清版动作类型的梦幻团队打造，完美融合顶级打斗动作与现代Roguelite元素，将经典奇幻街机游戏的氛围引入到原创世界塔拉姆大陆的沉浸式冒险当中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/16ac95e6586a8891dd6d65557de97660.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/16ac95e6586a8891dd6d65557de97660.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于巫师们的野心日益彰显，一场魔法灾难从天而降，普通民众对魔法失去信任，塔拉姆大陆经此浩劫，从此分崩离析。太阳王阿兹拉趁虚而入，利用这场恐慌，下令其座下腥红教团出击，妄图奴役一众巫师，还将忠心耿耿的王子们派往征服后的领土实施统治。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眼看阿兹拉的大军占据的领地越来越多，高阶女巫乌查维挺身而出，率领一小股叛军自阴影之中举起大旗，施展禁制魔法，挑战太阳王的专政，公然反抗他的绝对魔权。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/2f09c257ad1fd8dceeada28aed72c873.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/2f09c257ad1fd8dceeada28aed72c873.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/9ec0c3888ae0705cb3a64739b8e21432.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/9ec0c3888ae0705cb3a64739b8e21432.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识塔拉姆大陆的流亡英雄，每位英雄都各有独特的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加兰德拉自耶尔德勒姆的阴影之中现身，展现出无人能挡的自然力量。她挥舞巨剑，剑术精湛，招招夺命，并蕴含着令人胆寒、毁灭性的死灵之力。她平静的外表下，是几乎难以掩盖的滔天愤怒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡尔是塔拉姆大陆上最后一位自由矮人。他以祖传火铳和一双劲拳破敌，堪称近身格斗与爆破战术的大师。尽管在中程战中有所欠缺，但卡尔强悍的力量和敏捷的思维足以弥补缺陷，是反抗阿兹拉压迫的坚定盟友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场严峻考验之中，还会有两位神秘英雄加入阵列，共同展开推翻太阳王的任务，他们分别是布罗姆和神秘莫测的西德，前者是巫师界的天纵奇才，肩负着保护本族后裔的使命；后者则是一位敏锐的游击兵，不断在破碎的灵魂之中苦苦找寻答案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/da887b5e80618f414213d31269ba8063.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/da887b5e80618f414213d31269ba8063.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/75c987546fe409f6518a5f06b1696530.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/75c987546fe409f6518a5f06b1696530.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绝对魔权》将Dotemu和Guard Crush在清版动作游戏玩法方面的驾驭力与Supamonks顶尖的美术和动画制作能力合二为一。游戏不仅打斗节奏畅快，而且可重玩性强，挑战性十足，玩家可以尽情探索多条路径，面对难以预料的遭遇战，不断刷新游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/9d744b17b6987bc2133890f97d27006d.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/9d744b17b6987bc2133890f97d27006d.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/59c17a43d69f51b18ec6b5e7258203dc.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/59c17a43d69f51b18ec6b5e7258203dc.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合运用明快的连锁技和法术，使出原始而足具策略性的招式，击倒阿兹拉麾下的精锐守卫。利用魔法反击和稀有道具逆转局势，享受这套既考验技巧又讲究时机的战斗系统，每一次挑战都促使你制定新的战略，在敌阵中大杀四方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/5f4170dab2dc34a68c06d984371cf92f.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/5f4170dab2dc34a68c06d984371cf92f.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/5f4170dab2dc34a68c06d984371cf92f.mp4?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/82f1f9432f08884cf740f940ce2f0a6c.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/82f1f9432f08884cf740f940ce2f0a6c.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将化身孤胆英雄，揭竿而起，反抗阿兹拉的暴政，也可以在本地和在线联机模式中与朋友并肩作战。融合元素力量，同步施展攻击，就能化作令人咂舌的连锁技！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塔拉姆的世界堪称是一张错综复杂的挂毯，上面布满秘辛、故事和背叛。从格兰德里鎏金矿脉到贾罗巴苍翠森林，这场奇幻历险中，您踏过的每一步都有Gareth Coker （代表作《奥日与黑暗森林》、《光环：无限》、《波斯王子》）、北村友香（代表作《黑暗之魂》、《艾尔登法环》）和Mick Gordon （代表作《毁灭战士：永恒》、《原子之心》）等知名作曲家气势如虹的瑰丽配乐与您相伴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/284ec43594d6e860e981654b2c8d8642.poster.avif?t=1771265568\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904480/extras/284ec43594d6e860e981654b2c8d8642.webm?t=1771265568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>需要使用控制器才能启用本地多人游戏功能。</strong></i></p>",
